Package hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.nodes

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INodeVisitor
    Interface for class that visits a Node in a node tree structure and do an operation on him.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentNode
    This class is node representing an entire document.
    EchoNode
    This class is node representing a command which generates some textual output dynamically.
    EndNode
    Node representing end of for loop.
    ForLoopNode
    This class is node representing a single for-loop construct.
    Node
    This class represents base class for all graph nodes
    TextNode
    This class is node representing a piece of textual data.
